00:32:15,970 --> 00:32:18,371
And a lead magnet is just a little cookie that you give people

734
00:32:19,052 --> 00:32:21,313
to a little sweetener to have people join.

735
00:32:21,333 --> 00:32:24,476
It's just like that person at the office who has a little candy jar

736
00:32:24,516 --> 00:32:25,777
because they like to make conversation.

737
00:32:26,077 --> 00:32:29,439
And it's just a little bit of a little sweetener to get people to talk to you.

738
00:32:31,185 --> 00:32:33,567
And what these little sweeteners are

739
00:32:33,607 --> 00:32:35,349
is little cool gifts that you can get,

740
00:32:35,389 --> 00:32:38,411
like a soundtrack, you can beta access to your game,

741
00:32:38,691 --> 00:32:40,973
a free version of your game, like a demo.

