00:33:07,632 --> 00:33:12,094
And so you need that little bit of a sweetener just to get encourage those clicks onto your

753
00:33:12,114 --> 00:33:12,634
mailing list.

754
00:33:13,175 --> 00:33:14,916
That's why you need that lead magnet.

755
00:33:16,997 --> 00:33:19,058
