793
00:35:05,405 --> 00:35:08,186
you say, send this to them a day after they join my list.

794
00:35:08,366 --> 00:35:09,446
And then you write a second email.

795
00:35:09,866 --> 00:35:11,727
and you program it to go off the next day,

796
00:35:12,027 --> 00:35:13,607
and then a third one, the third day.

797
00:35:13,947 --> 00:35:15,728
So basically what you do is you're pre-writing

798
00:35:15,768 --> 00:35:17,008
a bunch of marketing messages.

799
00:35:17,388 --> 00:35:18,408
And so when they join your list,

800
00:35:18,588 --> 00:35:20,669
they're receiving those pre-programmed messages.

801
00:35:20,809 --> 00:35:22,269
